URL: https://api.vistara.io/api/mobile/tenants/{orgId}/users/{userId}/changePassword

METHOD: POST

HEADER:
	Authorization : Basic c3N2Ok5ldCF0aXZhbW81YjY=
	Content-Type : application/json
	Accept : application/json 

(ex: https://api.vistara.io/api/mobile/tenants/client_69919/users/USR0000002252/changePassword)

REQUEST:
........
{
 	"currentPassword":"Client@123",
 	"newPassword":"api123Test!",
 	"confirmPassword":"api123Test!"
}

RESPONSE:
.........
200 staus
 
Note: Encode username and password with colon(:) in between using Base64 algorithm.
base64_encode(loginName:password). Include this with 'Basic' prefix in Authorization header.	